---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
---

<Base title="Affiliate disclosure" description="How this site makes money, in plain language.">
  <section class="wrap prose">
    <h1 class="page-title">Affiliate disclosure</h1>
    <p>
      {SITE.name} is reader-supported. Some links on this site are affiliate links: if you
      click one and buy an eSIM or plan, we may earn a commission from the provider. This
      comes at <strong>no extra cost to you</strong> — you pay the same price either way.
    </p>
    <p>
      Commissions never influence our results. We buy every eSIM we review with our own
      money, run the same tests on all of them, and publish the numbers with dates and
      locations attached. Providers do not see reviews before publication and cannot pay
      for a better score or a higher ranking.
    </p>
    <p>
      If a page ever features a sponsored placement, it will be labelled clearly on that page.
    </p>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy: <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.contactEmail}</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-title { padding-top: 2rem; }
</style>
